---
title: Pan-seared Salmon and Cranberry Chutney with Roasted Squash and Green Beans
description: Celebrate the holidays with juicy fresh salmon filets, tender sweet roasted squash and a savoury tart cranberry chutney! It's a simple, elegant meal that is just as beautiful as it is satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-poele-et-chutney-de-canneberges-200424af.jpg
